<p class="ayah 82-19" id="19" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(The) Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَمْلِكُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will have power</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَفْسٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a soul</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّنَفْسٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for a soul</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَيْــًٔا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">anything,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَمْرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the Command</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَئِذٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّلَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) with Allah.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>19<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
